          "text": "**Implementing rot13 function**\n\nI want to create a function that implements the ROT13 cipher efficiently. It should match the signature for `unsigned char rot13(unsigned char c)`. I'll focus on correctly rotating lowercase and uppercase letters. \n\nMy plan involves checking if the character is in the ranges 'a'-'z' or 'A'-'Z' and applying the appropriate transformation. The code will handle the rotation using simple conditions for each case. I\u2019ll keep it straightforward to ensure it's easily compilable.",
